Package net.ognyanov.niogram.analysis

Grammar analysis tools

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AttributeCalculator
    An interface for classes which calculate attributes of a grammar.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FirstFollowCalculator
    A calculator for First/Follow sets and the related conflicts data.
    FirstKFollowKCalculator
    A calculator for FirstK/FollowK sets and the related conflicts data.
    FirstKLFollowKLCalculator
    A calculator for FirstKL/FollowKL sets and the related conflicts data.
    FirstKLTrace
    A trace for a terminal in the FirstKL set of a node.
    FirstKTrace
    A trace for a terminal in the FirstK set of a node.
    FirstTrace
    A trace for a terminal in the First set of a node.
    FlagsCalculator
    A calculator for the basic flag attributes of a grammar : the nullability of all nodes and the productivity, reachability and use of the nonterminal rules.
    FollowKLTrace
    A trace for a terminal in the FollowKL set of a node.
    FollowKTrace
    A trace for a terminal in the FollowK set of a node.
    FollowTrace
    A trace for a terminal in the Follow set of a node.
    GraphAnalysis
    A facility for building and analyzing dependency graphs of grammars.
